text:
Rinze, good work.
How are you feeling?

Because Producer-sama...
Is by my side...

No, I'm sorry I can't do more.
But if you have any trouble, please tell me.

Well...
I'm not exactly in trouble...

If you have time...
I'd like to walk together... nearby...

Ah... too much focus on lessons can be suffocating.
Got it.

Then, during the next break,
Let's take a walk outside.
